                    <span class="font-bold text-slate-900">Does LLM Arena pay dividends?</span>
                    <span x-text="active === 3 ? '−' : '+'" class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-400"></span>
                </button>
                <div x-show="active === 3" class="px-6 py-4 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
